{
  "stem": "15115.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you talk to-- if you were to talk to any Canadian, they won't believe it anyway.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What they know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came over here, they thought we are greenhorns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the meantime, the Canadians that were here, they were the greenhorns, because we-- they took us to a house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Says, oh, you know, this is a radio.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, you-- comes the voice, comes from a radio-- like we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew what a radio was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One of my friends says, is there somebody underneath it that talking to-- you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The people that were here-- the people that were here, they came in the 18th-- in 1918.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't have anything, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whatever they had over here, they thought that still, in Europe, it's still the same.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But Europe wasn't the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had the same thing in Europe that the people in Toronto had, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they-- and those were non-educated people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They all left because they didn't want to go to the army, or they have pogroms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had pogroms in Poland, in Ukrainian, and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They'd all run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came over here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were all-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] working here for $4 a week, working tailors, and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some of the people were nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of the people, they thought that we-- we are coming in from where they came.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we-- we already saw so much during the war that our eyes-- we became experienced in almost-- in anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You take it in the countries around-- surround us, Europe surround us, the food, the electricity, the radios, the TVs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, we have no TVs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean the telephones, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
